title: Cosmic Queries - The Science of Love
description: What’s love got to do with it? Find out in our Valentine’s Day edition of Cosmic Queries when co-host Chuck Nice gets down on his knees and pops your questions to Neil deGrasse Tyson and biological anthropologist Dr. Helen Fisher.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
